-1 grey elf elves greyelf greyelves~

Grey Elves are the most common of all the elven races.  They have a long
life-span, but often fail to live to longevity because of their curious and
adventurous nature.  They are the most interactive and social of the elves. 
Grey elves tend not to trust the unpredictability magic, and so make poor
mages.  They best fair in the cunning arts of thievry and assasination, but
are adequate at any class.  As typical elves, they are granted infravision
and sneak at birth.  They are also, of course, vulnerable to iron and
resistant to charm.  Their  maximum stats are : 
Str(15)  Int(21)  Wis(18)  Dex(19)  Con(15)
Greyelves start with 5 CP(Creation Points).
 
