note read to scroll through them one at a time.

Six other note directories exist, these are ideas, news, changes, rpnote,
qnote, and penalties (imms only).  They are used the exact same way, for 
example idea read 5 will read idea #5.  Posting to the news and changes boards
is restricted. The 'unread' command can be used to show your unread notes on
