-1 VAMPIRES~

Vampires have the ability to drink the blood of their prey.  They gain
life force from this blood, hence forth Blood Points.  Blood is the life
force of a vampire.  Blood grants a vampire partial immortality, so when you
reach 0 hp, if you have more than 6 bp, you will be reducded to 3 bp and you
