assasins, though they are well-rounded and skilled at any class.  Through
the ages, the Drow have mastered immunity to disease and resistance to
poison.  Their evil souls are vulnerable to holy, light, and fire.  Their
dark ruthlessness has enabled them with the ability to cause enhanced damage
