0 HITDICE~

A high number of dice makes for less variance in mobiles hitpoints.
Suggested values are:

       level:     dice         min         max        mean
         1:       1d2+6       7(  7)     8(   8)     8(   8)
	 2:       1d3+15     16( 15)    18(  18)    17(  17)
	 3:       1d6+24     25( 24)    30(  30)    27(  27)
